detailedDescription.articleBody: Sir Keir Rodney Starmer KCB QC MP is a British politician and former lawyer who has served as Leader of the Labour Party and Leader of the Opposition since 2020. He has been Member of Parliament for Holborn and St Pancras since 2015.

detailedDescription.articleBody: Mary Soames, Baroness Soames, LG, DBE, FRSL was a British author. The youngest of the five children of Winston Churchill and his wife, Clementine, she worked for multiple public organisations including the Red Cross and the Women's Voluntary Service from 1939 to 1941, and joined the Auxiliary Territorial Service in 1941.
detailedDescription.articleBodyHi: मैरी सोम्स, बैरोनेस सोम्स, एलजी, डीबीई, एफआरएसएल एक ब्रिटिश लेखिका थीं, विंस्टन चर्चिल और उनकी पत्नी क्लेमेंटाइन के पांच बच्चों में सबसे छोटी, उन्होंने 1939 से 1941 तक रेड क्रॉस और महिला स्वैच्छिक सेवा सहित कई सार्वजनिक संगठनों के लिए काम किया।

detailedDescription.articleBody: Microsoft Corporation is an American multinational technology company with headquarters in Redmond, Washington. It develops, manufactures, licenses, supports, and sells computer software, consumer electronics, personal computers, and related services.
detailedDescription.articleBodyHi: Microsoft Corporation एक अमेरिकी बहुराष्ट्रीय प्रौद्योगिकी कंपनी है जिसका मुख्यालय रेडमंड, वाशिंगटन में है, यह कंप्यूटर सॉफ्टवेयर, उपभोक्ता इलेक्ट्रॉनिक्स, व्यक्तिगत कंप्यूटर और संबंधित सेवाओं का विकास, निर्माण, लाइसेंस, समर्थन और बिक्री करता है,
